# Network Enumeration Using Nmap

## Objective
The goal of this lab was to perform network enumeration on a target machine using Nmap to identify open ports, running services, and potential vulnerabilities.

## Scenario
I was given access to a target machine and needed to gather as much information as possible about the system without logging into it.

## Tools Used
- Nmap

